      <title>哈里斯计划下周在华盛顿与泽连斯基会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/harris-plans-meeting-with-zelenskiy-in-washington-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，民主党候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯计划下周在华盛顿会见乌克兰总统泽连斯基，以拓宽她的外交政策形象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/harris-plans-meeting-with-zelenskiy-in-washington-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 00:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
